{"tid":1425408,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"機電工程署 激光產品安全指引","createTime":"2019-08-06T18:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T18:14:57.000Z","uid":298549,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d0eb134876f06bd5519b37d39ca728627908ff40","tid":1425408,"uid":298549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:06:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.emsd.gov.hk/tc/other_regulatory_services/laser_safety/publications/safety_guidelines_for_laser_products/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.emsd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fother_regulatory_services%2Flaser_safety%2Fpublications%2Fsafety_guidelines_for_laser_products%2Findex.html&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZiLieoVo5Z%2Bt8AyiqwqBN0Y%3D&h=02d6b677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.emsd.gov.hk/tc/other_regulatory_services/laser_safety/publications/safety_guidelines_for_laser_products/index.html</a><br />\n機電工程署 激光產品安全指引<br />\n備用<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>安全指引</strong></ins><br />\n<strong>第1、1M、2、2M、3R、3B及4類激光產品</strong><br />\n不可直視激光光束<br />\n不可將激光光束瞄準任何人的眼睛<br />\n確保激光產品上貼有適當的說明及警告標記，如果產品的尺寸或設計使標記無法貼在產品上，則標記必須附在使用者說明書內或包裝箱上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>保護眼罩 第3R、3B及4類激光產品的額外安全措施</strong><br />\n遵守產品操作手冊所列的指引<br />\n僱用合資格或已受訓的人員保養及維修激光產品<br />\n操作或維修中、高功率激光產品時，應使用適當的保護眼罩及穿着適當的保護衣物<br />\n在可能受到中、高功率激光照射的地方張貼適當的警告告示<br />\n訓練有關員工正確及安全使用激光產品"},{"pid":"8edc23896e7522cad2ddb9ec6cb63fe3cf2d48fe","tid":1425408,"uid":61680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:14:57.000Z","msg":"係時候試下新功能<br />\n<br />\n不推文回覆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}